## Perubahan yang Diusulkan

### Backend (Laravel)

#### [MODIFY] [AdminDashboardController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/Admin/AdminDashboardController.php)
- Menambahkan method `getDashboardInit` untuk mengeksekusi logika metrik, reality-check, dan logs secara berurutan:
  ```php
  public function getDashboardInit(Request $request)
  {
      $metrics = $this->getMetricsData(); // Refactor getMetrics ke private helper
      $realityCheck = $this->getRealityCheckData(); // Refactor getRealityCheck ke private helper
      $arimaLogs = app(\App\Http\Controllers\Admin\ArimaController::class)->getLogsData();

      return response()->json([
          'metrics_data' => $metrics,
          'reality_check_data' => $realityCheck,
          'arima_logs' => $arimaLogs
      ]);
  }
  ```

#### [MODIFY] [api.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/routes/api.php)
- Menambahkan rute GET `/dashboard/init` di bawah admin group prefix.

#### [MODIFY] [StorefrontController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/StorefrontController.php)
- Mengubah method `getProducts` agar melakukan cache hasil paginasi berdasarkan parameter request:
  ```php
  $page = $request->get('page', 1);
  $category = $request->get('category', '');
  $keyword = $request->get('keyword', '');
  $sort = $request->get('sort', 'newest');

  $cacheKey = "storefront_products_p_{$page}_c_{$category}_s_{$sort}_k_{$keyword}";

  $products = Cache::remember($cacheKey, 60, function () use ($query) {
      return $query->paginate(12);
  });
  ```

#### [MODIFY] [PosController.php](file:///c:/laragon/www/Diana_fashion/diana_fashion_app/app/Http/Controllers/PosController.php)
- Mengubah method `searchProducts` agar menerapkan caching 1 menit pada data pencarian produk:
  ```php
  $keyword = $request->get('keyword', '');
  $category = $request->get('category', '');

  $cacheKey = "pos_products_k_{$keyword}_c_{$category}";

  $products = Cache::remember($cacheKey, 60, function () use ($query, $request) {
      if (!$request->filled('keyword') && !$request->filled('category')) {
          return $query->orderBy('created_at', 'desc')->take(15)->get();
      }
      return $query->get();
  });
  ```

